window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Life is full of surprises...even when you’re already dead.</b> </p> <p>Sterling has his hands full balancing the attentions of an ancient Norse deity, a knife-wielding Knight of the Flowers, and a sleazy vampire sycophant. And those are just his buddies.</p> <p>But something is amiss in sleepy Silveropolis. More human hunters are appearing, intent on attacking not only Sterling, but the rest of the supernatural population as well. Stranger still is the sudden disappearance of the moon. With the local werewolf pack weakened and the mountains swarming with hunters, Sterling and his friends have their work cut out for them. Except there’s another tiny problem.</p> <p>The Scepter of the vampire court of California is in town. And she is pissed.</p>"; 
